OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A number of workers at the RNLI have   
OL,6, raised some concerns about sexist and  
OL,7, bigoted behaviour at the organisation. 
OL,9,FInternal surveys from 2021 and 2022 on 
OL,10,Fthe attitudes of staff and volunteers  
OL,11,Fworking at the UK lifeboat charity cite
OL,12,Fsexism and bullying.                   
OL,14,FThe documents, first reported by the   
OL,15,FTimes, have been seen by the BBC.      
OL,17,FThe RNLI told the BBC it was sorry to  
OL,18,Fanyone who had faced "behaviours and   
OL,19,Factions that no one should have to     
OL,20,Ftolerate" and "will act".              
